data.description: Does the January blues already have you longing a new home with a beautiful large yard? This neat split level home has everything you need. The original wood charm throughout will make you feel right at home upon entering the front door. A cozy living room, dining room, kitchen, bedroom/craftroom and a full bathroom complete the main level, while another 3 bedrooms and full bathroom can be found upstairs. The primary suite is located up just a few steps and has a private dressing room with vanity attached to bathroom and closet. You can also find a 1/2 bath, full wet bar and laundry room downstairs. This is a great family room area, game room or make it another primary suite. The backyard is perfect for adding a swimming pool or that pergola you have always dreamed of with a hot tub. New windows in 2021, Main level HVAC in 2023, Upstairs HVAC in 2021 and downstairs mini split in 2019. Metal roof approx. 2011 and septic pumped/inspected in 2020. Its ready for new owners to call it home!
